						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2765e39" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Contract coverage of transportation; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2765e48" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Instructions to the contractor to minimize the ultimate transportation costs to the Government.</p>
						            </li>
